I have to go over the
story once more. Why?

01:19:53.200 --> 01:19:55.919
Because it still
needs editing, damn you.

01:19:56.000 --> 01:19:58.912
All this fucking intelligence
jargon is hurting our brains.

01:19:59.000 --> 01:20:02.675
This PRISM story is
still incomprehensible.

