PRISM is the second story,
Janine.

01:20:04.360 --> 01:20:06.157
Verizon is the first story.

01:20:06.280 --> 01:20:08.794
Have it ready to post by 4:00 p. m.,
5:00 at the latest.

01:20:08.880 --> 01:20:10.108
Ugh...

