I built it.

01:24:07.280 --> 01:24:08.474
You?
Yeah.

01:24:09.480 --> 01:24:11.376
You know I've actually...
I've been thinking about, uh,

01:24:11.400 --> 01:24:13.550
another use
for Epic Shelter.

01:24:13.640 --> 01:24:14.675
What'd you have
in mind?

01:24:15.560 --> 01:24:17.596
Well, I was chatting
with Jim Lowell

01:24:17.680 --> 01:24:18.736
about how there's
so many programs...

01:24:18.760 --> 01:24:19.795
Deputy Director Lowell?

01:24:19.880 --> 01:24:22.030
Yeah. Yeah.

01:24:22.160 --> 01:24:24.355
And we were saying there's
so many programs nowadays,

01:24:24.440 --> 01:24:26.536
it's kind of impossible to keep
track of them anymore, right?

01:24:26.560 --> 01:24:29.233
So why not create
a centralized database.

01:24:29.640 --> 01:24:31.073
Ah. Like an index.

